TITLE: Episode 37 - Waco pt. 3 of 3 Judgment Day (MLGA recast)
DESCRIPTION: Two days ago was the 27th anniversary of the slaughter of the Branch Davidians in Waco, Texas. Today, I am sharing the final episode of a three part miniseries about those events. It is a recast from the Make Liberty Great Again podcast. This will blow your mind.
